parameters: Clea: It's nostalgic... the place where I met Celis-san.

Clea: And this is the place where I swore to become an
adventurer.

Clea: Celis-san should be at the place where we made a
promise.

Do you want to enter the deepest part of the Adventurer's
Cave?
Clea (Let's make sure we're mentally prepared first)

Clea (Someday, we'll talk about our dreams here... Even
though I don't even know who I am, do I have the
qualifications?)

Clea (My body is trembling, because I don't want to be
disappointed)

Priestess Sophia: Your greatsword is meant to carve out
tomorrow for someone... and for yourself as well. Keep
carving out your own tomorrow.

Mage Relm: Mmm, yes, let's play again... Thank you for
becoming my first friend...

Thief Nora: Cool, weak, strong, and timid... No matter what
kind of Clea-san, I love all of them, all of them!
Clea: My friends always support me when I'm weak.
Clea: Let's go, let's carve out our path.
Clea (Let's head towards the back of the cave now)
